{"lemma":"ضامِن","slug":"ضامِن","root":"ض.م.ن","root_slug":"ض-م-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-م-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26049"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B6%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%90%D9%86"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26049","headword_ar":"ضَامِنٌ","root":"Dmn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamiynN","text_ar":"ضَمِينٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"One who is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"responsible, answerable, accountable, amenable, surety,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"guarantee:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K:) both are mentioned by IAar as syn., like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAminN","text_ar":"سَامِنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samiynN","text_ar":"سَمِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) God is represented by the Prophet as saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano xaraja mujaAhidFA fiY sabiyliY waA@botigaA='i maroDaAtiY faA^anaA","text_ar":"مَنْ خَرَجَ مُجَاهِدًا فِى سَبِيلِى وَا@بْتِغَا=ءِ مَرْضَاتِى فَاَنَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi DaAminN wahuwa EalaY~a DaAminN","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ ضَامِنٌ وَهُوَ عَلَىَّ ضَامِنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whoso goes forth as a warrior in my cause, and seeking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seeking earnestly, to obtain my approval,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I am responsible to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"for what I have promised him, to recompense him living and dead;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DAmn","text_ar":"ضامن"},{"kind":"text","text":"being made trans. by means of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ElY","text_ar":"على"},{"kind":"text","text":"because it implies the meaning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHaAmK","text_ar":"مُحَامٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiybN","text_ar":"رَقِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the last clause means nearly the same, but is rendered as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and he is one who has"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a claim to"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"responsibility on my part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though care and mindfulness [of him] were obligatory on me. (Mgh.) And it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_imaAmu DaAminN","text_ar":"الاـِمَامُ ضَامِنٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAlmuw^a*~inu muw^otamanN","text_ar":"وَالمُوَذِّنُ مُوْتَمَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh, JM, * TA:) [the latter clause has been expl. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^mn","text_ar":"امن"},{"kind":"text","text":"(voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amiynN","text_ar":"اَمِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"):] the former clause means,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The imám"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leader of prayer"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is as though he were responsible for the correctness of the prayer of those who follow him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JM, TA: [and the like is said, with other, similar, explanations, in the Mgh:]) or it means,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the imám is careful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mindful, for the people"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who follow him"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the correctness of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their prayer."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAminN","text_ar":"ضَامِنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miDomaAnN","text_ar":"مِضْمَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a she-camel, signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having a fœtus in her belly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the pls. are"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DawaAminu","text_ar":"ضَوَامِنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDaAmiynu","text_ar":"مَضَامِينُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IAar, L and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lqH","text_ar":"لقح"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in the present art.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAminapN","text_ar":"ضَامِنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to rights, or dues, ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huquwq","text_ar":"حُقُوق"},{"kind":"text","text":",) is used by Lebeed as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDomuwnapN","text_ar":"مَضْمُونَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDomuwnN","text_ar":"مَضْمُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHilapN","text_ar":"رَاحِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maroHuwlapN","text_ar":"مَرْحُولَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K"]}]}}